{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I have, like, a thing about sleeping."},{"time":2000,"text":"I don't sleep that much,"},{"time":4000,"text":"and I've come to this thing about, like, not sleeping much"},{"time":7000,"text":"as being a great virtue, after years of kind of"},{"time":9000,"text":"battling it as being a terrible detriment, or something."},{"time":11000,"text":"And now I really like sort of sitting up, you know."},{"time":14000,"text":"But for years I've been sitting up"},{"time":17000,"text":"and I think that, like, my creativity is greatly motivated by this kind of insomnia."},{"time":23000,"text":"I lie awake. I think thoughts. I walk aimlessly."},{"time":28000,"text":"Sometimes I used to walk more at night."},{"time":30000,"text":"I walk during the day and I follow people who I think look interesting."},{"time":34000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":36000,"text":"And sometimes -- actually, once it was on Page Six in the Post,"},{"time":40000,"text":"that I was cruising this guy, like, sort of, whatever,"},{"time":43000,"text":"but I was actually just following because he had these really great shoes on."},{"time":46000,"text":"And so I was following this guy."},{"time":49000,"text":"And I took a picture of his shoes,"},{"time":50000,"text":"and we thanked each other and just went on our way."},{"time":52000,"text":"But I do that all the time."},{"time":53000,"text":"As a matter of fact, I think a lot of my design ideas"},{"time":57000,"text":"come from mistakes and tricks of the eye."},{"time":61000,"text":"Because I feel like, you know, there are so many images out there,"},{"time":65000,"text":"so many clothes out there."},{"time":68000,"text":"And the only ones that look interesting to me"},{"time":70000,"text":"are the ones that look slightly mistaken, of course,"},{"time":74000,"text":"or very, very surprising."},{"time":76000,"text":"And often, I'm driving in a taxi"},{"time":78000,"text":"and I see a hole in a shirt, or something"},{"time":80000,"text":"that looks very interesting or pretty or functional"},{"time":83000,"text":"in some way that I'd never seen happen before."},{"time":87000,"text":"And so I'd make the car stop, and I'd get out of the car and walk,"},{"time":91000,"text":"and see that in fact there wasn't a hole, but it was a trick of my eye,"},{"time":94000,"text":"it was a shadow, you know."},{"time":96000,"text":"Or if there was a hole I'd think like, oh damn,"},{"time":98000,"text":"there was actually someone thought of that thought already."},{"time":100000,"text":"Someone made that mistake already so I can't do it anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"I don't know where inspiration comes from."},{"time":107000,"text":"It does not come for me from research."},{"time":111000,"text":"I don't get necessarily inspired by research."},{"time":113000,"text":"As a matter of fact, one of the most fun things"},{"time":115000,"text":"I've ever, ever done in my whole life,"},{"time":117000,"text":"was this Christmas season at the Guggenheim in New York."},{"time":121000,"text":"I read \"Peter and the Wolf\" with this beautiful band from Juilliard."},{"time":125000,"text":"And I did like, you know, the narrator, and I read it."},{"time":127000,"text":"And I saw this really smart critic who I love."},{"time":130000,"text":"This woman, Joan Acocella, who's a friend of mine,"},{"time":132000,"text":"and she came backstage and she said,"},{"time":133000,"text":"oh, you know, Isaac, did you know that, talking about Stalinism"},{"time":136000,"text":"and talking about, you know, like the '30s in Russia."},{"time":139000,"text":"And I said, how do I know about Stalinism?"},{"time":142000,"text":"I know about a wolf and a bird and, you know,"},{"time":144000,"text":"he ate the bird, and then in the end you hear, you know,"},{"time":147000,"text":"you hear the bird squeaking, or something, you know?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"So I don't really know that. I don't really --"},{"time":152000,"text":"actually I do my own kind of research, you know."},{"time":155000,"text":"If I'm commissioned to do the costumes for an 18th-century opera, or something like that,"},{"time":160000,"text":"I will do a lot of research, because it's interesting,"},{"time":163000,"text":"not because it's what I'm supposed to do."},{"time":165000,"text":"I'm very, very, very inspired by movies."},{"time":168000,"text":"The color of movies and the way light makes the colors,"},{"time":172000,"text":"light from behind the projection,"},{"time":174000,"text":"or light from the projection, makes the colors look so impossible."},{"time":179000,"text":"And anyway, roll this little clip, I'll just show you."},{"time":182000,"text":"I sit up at night and I watch movies"},{"time":185000,"text":"and I watch women in movies a lot."},{"time":188000,"text":"And I think about, you know, their roles,"},{"time":191000,"text":"and about how you have to, like, watch what your daughters look at."},{"time":195000,"text":"Because I look at the way women are portrayed all the time."},{"time":199000,"text":"Whether they're kind of glorified in this way,"},{"time":202000,"text":"or whether they're kind of, you know, ironically glorified,"},{"time":207000,"text":"or whether they're, you know, sort of denigrated, or ironically denigrated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":213000,"text":"I go back to color all the time."},{"time":215000,"text":"Color is something that motivates me a lot."},{"time":219000,"text":"It's rarely color that I find in nature,"},{"time":225000,"text":"although, you know, juxtaposed next to artificial color,"},{"time":231000,"text":"natural color is so beautiful."},{"time":233000,"text":"So that's what I do. I study color a lot."},{"time":235000,"text":"But for the most part, I think, like, how can I ever make anything"},{"time":242000,"text":"that is as beautiful as that image of Natalie Wood?"},{"time":245000,"text":"How can I ever make anything as beautiful as Greta Garbo?"},{"time":249000,"text":"I mean, that's just not possible, you know."},{"time":253000,"text":"And so that's what makes me lie awake at night, I guess, you know."},{"time":257000,"text":"I want to show you -- I'm also like a big --"},{"time":260000,"text":"I go to astrologers and tarot card readers often,"},{"time":264000,"text":"and that's another thing that motivates me a lot."},{"time":266000,"text":"People say, oh, do that. An astrologer tells me to do something."},{"time":270000,"text":"So I do it."},{"time":271000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":272000,"text":"When I was about 21, an astrologer told me"},{"time":276000,"text":"that I was going to meet the man of my dreams,"},{"time":278000,"text":"and that his name was going to be Eric, right?"},{"time":281000,"text":"So, you know, for years I would go to bars"},{"time":283000,"text":"and, sort of, anyone I met whose name was Eric"},{"time":285000,"text":"I was humping immediately, or something."},{"time":288000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":290000,"text":"And there were times when I was actually so desperate"},{"time":291000,"text":"I would just, you know, walk into a room and just go like, \"Eric!\""},{"time":293000,"text":"And anybody who would turn around I would, sort of, make a beeline for."},{"time":295000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":298000,"text":"And I had this really interesting tarot reading a long time ago."},{"time":302000,"text":"The last card he pulled, which was representing my destiny"},{"time":305000,"text":"was this guy on like a straw boater with a cane"},{"time":307000,"text":"and you know, sort of spats and this, you know, a minstrel singer, right?"},{"time":311000,"text":"I want to show you this clip because I do this kind of crazy thing"},{"time":313000,"text":"where I do a cabaret act."},{"time":316000,"text":"So actually, check this out."},{"time":318000,"text":"Very embarrassing."},{"time":320000,"text":"(Video): Thank you. We can do anything you ask."}]},{"cues":[{"time":323000,"text":"The name of the show is based on this story"},{"time":329000,"text":"that I have to tell you about my mother."},{"time":330000,"text":"It's sort of an excerpt from a quote of hers."},{"time":333000,"text":"I was dating this guy, right?"},{"time":334000,"text":"And this has to do with being happy, I swear."},{"time":338000,"text":"I was dating this guy and it was going on for about a year, right."},{"time":344000,"text":"And we were getting serious,"},{"time":345000,"text":"so we decided to invite them all to dinner, our parents."},{"time":347000,"text":"And we, you know, sort of introduced them to each other."},{"time":348000,"text":"My mother was, sort of, very sensitive to his mother,"},{"time":352000,"text":"who it seemed was a little bit skeptical about the whole alternative lifestyle thing."},{"time":357000,"text":"You know, homosexuality, right?"},{"time":359000,"text":"So my mother was a little offended. She turned to her and she said,"},{"time":361000,"text":"\"Are you kidding? They have the greatest life together."},{"time":364000,"text":"They eat out, they see shows.\""},{"time":367000,"text":"They eat out, they see shows."},{"time":369000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":371000,"text":"That's the name of the show, they eat out, they --"},{"time":372000,"text":"that's on my tombstone when I die."},{"time":374000,"text":"\"He ate out, he saw shows,\" right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":380000,"text":"So in editing these clips, I didn't have the audacity"},{"time":383000,"text":"to edit a clip of me singing at Joe's Pub."},{"time":387000,"text":"So you'll have to, like, go check it out and come see me or something."},{"time":389000,"text":"Because it's mortifying, and yet it feels ..."},{"time":395000,"text":"I don't know how to put this."},{"time":396000,"text":"I feel as little comfort as possible is a good thing, you know."},{"time":402000,"text":"And at least, you know, in my case,"},{"time":406000,"text":"because if I just do one thing all the time,"},{"time":409000,"text":"I don't know, I get very, very bored. I bore very easily."},{"time":415000,"text":"And you know, I don't say that I do everything well,"},{"time":421000,"text":"I just say that I do a lot of things, that's all."},{"time":424000,"text":"And I kind of try not to look back, you know."},{"time":428000,"text":"Except, I guess, that's what staying up every night is about."},{"time":431000,"text":"Like, looking back and thinking, what a fool you made of yourself, you know."},{"time":435000,"text":"But I guess that's okay. Right?"},{"time":439000,"text":"Because if you do many things"},{"time":440000,"text":"you get to feel lousy about everything,"},{"time":442000,"text":"and not just one, you know."},{"time":444000,"text":"You don't master feeling lousy about one thing."},{"time":447000,"text":"Yeah, exactly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":450000,"text":"I will show you this next thing,"},{"time":453000,"text":"speaking of costumes for operas."},{"time":454000,"text":"I do work with different choreographers."},{"time":456000,"text":"I work with Twyla Tharp a lot,"},{"time":458000,"text":"and I work with Mark Morris a lot,"},{"time":460000,"text":"who is one of my best friends."},{"time":461000,"text":"And I designed three operas with him,"},{"time":465000,"text":"and the most recent one, \"King Arthur.\""},{"time":468000,"text":"I'd been very ingrained in the dance world"},{"time":470000,"text":"since I was a teenager."},{"time":471000,"text":"I went to performing arts high school,"},{"time":473000,"text":"where I was an actor."},{"time":474000,"text":"And many of my friends were ballet dancers."},{"time":477000,"text":"Again, I don't know where inspiration comes from."},{"time":480000,"text":"I don't know where it comes from."},{"time":483000,"text":"I started making puppets when I was a kid."},{"time":485000,"text":"Maybe that's where the whole inspiration thing started from, puppets, right."},{"time":489000,"text":"And then performing arts high school."},{"time":492000,"text":"There I was in high school,"},{"time":493000,"text":"meeting dancers and acting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495000,"text":"And somehow, from there, I got interested in design."},{"time":499000,"text":"I went to Parsons School of Design"},{"time":502000,"text":"and then I began my career as a designer."},{"time":505000,"text":"I don't really think of myself as a designer,"},{"time":507000,"text":"I don't really think of myself necessarily as a fashion designer."},{"time":510000,"text":"And frankly, I don't really know what to call myself."},{"time":512000,"text":"I think of myself as a ... I don't know what I think of myself as."},{"time":517000,"text":"It's just that."},{"time":518000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":522000,"text":"But I must say, this whole thing about being slightly bored all the time,"},{"time":526000,"text":"that is what -- I think that is a very important thing for a fashion designer."},{"time":529000,"text":"You always have to be slightly bored with everything."},{"time":532000,"text":"And if you're not, you have to pretend to be slightly bored with everything."},{"time":535000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":537000,"text":"But I am really a little bored with everything."},{"time":539000,"text":"I always say to my partner, Marisa Gardini, who books everything --"},{"time":543000,"text":"she books everything and she makes everything happen."},{"time":545000,"text":"And she makes all the deals."},{"time":547000,"text":"And I always tell her that I find myself"},{"time":549000,"text":"with a lot of time on the computer bridge program."},{"time":552000,"text":"Too much time on computer bridge, which is, you know, like that's"},{"time":558000,"text":"so ... somehow, like, about ten years ago"},{"time":561000,"text":"I thought that the most unboring place in the world"},{"time":564000,"text":"would be like a T.V. studio,"},{"time":566000,"text":"like for a day show. Some kind of day talk show."},{"time":568000,"text":"Because it's all of these things that I love"},{"time":572000,"text":"all kind of in one place."},{"time":573000,"text":"And if you ever get bored you can look at another thing,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and do another thing and talk about it, right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":579000,"text":"And so I had this T.V. show."},{"time":581000,"text":"And that was a very, very, very big part of my process."},{"time":584000,"text":"Actually, could you roll the clip, please?"},{"time":586000,"text":"This is one of my favorite clips of Rosie."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588000,"text":"(Video) Isaac Mizrahi: We're back on the set."},{"time":590000,"text":"Hi there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":591000,"text":"Rosie O'Donnell: Hello, Ben."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592000,"text":"IM: Look how cute she looks with this, just a slick back."}]},{"cues":[{"time":593000,"text":"Man: Her grandmother says, \"Delish!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":595000,"text":"IM: Ah, wow, delish. All right. So now where should I position myself?"},{"time":601000,"text":"I want to stay out of the way."},{"time":602000,"text":"I don't want to be -- okay. Here we go."},{"time":604000,"text":"Do you get nervous, Ashleigh?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":606000,"text":"Ashleigh: Doing what?"},{"time":607000,"text":"ROD: Cutting hair."}]},{"cues":[{"time":608000,"text":"A: Cutting hair? Never, never."},{"time":609000,"text":"I don't think there was ever a day where I cut hair I was nervous."},{"time":612000,"text":"IM: You look so cute already, by the way."},{"time":613000,"text":"ROD: You like it? All right."},{"time":615000,"text":"IM: Do you have a problem with looking cute? You want to look cute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":616000,"text":"ROD: Of course I want to look cute."},{"time":618000,"text":"IM: Just checking, because some people want to look, you know,"},{"time":619000,"text":"aggressively ugly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620000,"text":"ROD: No, not me, no."}]},{"cues":[{"time":621000,"text":"IM: You read about all these people who have a lot of money"},{"time":625000,"text":"and they have kids and the kids always end up somehow, like,"},{"time":628000,"text":"really messed up, you know what I mean?"},{"time":630000,"text":"And there's got to be some way to do that, Rosie."},{"time":633000,"text":"Because just because if you're fabulously rich, and fabulously famous,"},{"time":637000,"text":"does that mean you shouldn't have kids,"},{"time":639000,"text":"because you know they're going to end up getting messed up?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":640000,"text":"ROD: No, but it means that your priority has to be"},{"time":642000,"text":"their well-being first, I think."},{"time":645000,"text":"But you have to make the decision for yourself."},{"time":647000,"text":"My kids are seven, who the hell knows."},{"time":649000,"text":"They're going to be like 14 and in rehab."},{"time":651000,"text":"And they're going to be playing this clip:"},{"time":652000,"text":"\"I'm such a good mother.\""},{"time":656000,"text":"My God, this is the shortest I've ever had."}]},{"cues":[{"time":658000,"text":"IM: It looks good, yeah?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":659000,"text":"A: I was going to ask you, has your hair ever been --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":660000,"text":"ROD: No! It's all right -- go crazy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":662000,"text":"IM: I feel like it needs to be a little closer down here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664000,"text":"A: Oh no, we're just staging,"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666000,"text":"ROD: We're just staging it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667000,"text":"IM: Are you freaking out? You look so cute."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668000,"text":"ROD: No, I love it. It's the new me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"IM: Oh, it's so fabulous!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":671000,"text":"ROD: Flock of Rosie. Wooo!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":675000,"text":"IM: So by the way. Of all the most unboring things in the world, right."},{"time":680000,"text":"I mean, like making someone who's already cute look terrible like that."},{"time":684000,"text":"That is not boring. That is nothing if it's not boring."},{"time":688000,"text":"Actually, I read this great quote the other day, which was,"},{"time":693000,"text":"\"Style makes you feel great because it takes your mind off the fact that you're going to die.\""},{"time":698000,"text":"Right? And then I realized, that was on my website,"},{"time":703000,"text":"and then it said, like, you know, the quote was attributed to me"},{"time":705000,"text":"and I thought, oh, I said something, you know, in an interview."},{"time":707000,"text":"I forgot that I said that. But it's really true."}]},{"cues":[{"time":711000,"text":"I want to show you this last clip because it's going to be my last goodbye."},{"time":715000,"text":"I'll tell you that I cook a lot also. I love to cook."},{"time":718000,"text":"And I often look at things as though they're food."},{"time":721000,"text":"Like I say, oh, you know, would you serve a rotten chicken?"},{"time":724000,"text":"Then how could you serve, you know, a beat up old dress or something."},{"time":726000,"text":"How could you show a beat up old dress?"},{"time":727000,"text":"I always relate things to kitchen-ry."},{"time":732000,"text":"And so I think that's what it all boils down to."},{"time":736000,"text":"Everything boils down to that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":737000,"text":"So check this out."},{"time":738000,"text":"This is what I've been doing because I think it's the most fun thing in the world."},{"time":741000,"text":"It's, like, this website."},{"time":742000,"text":"It's got a lot of different things on it."},{"time":744000,"text":"It's a polymathematical website."},{"time":746000,"text":"We actually shoot segments like T.V. show segments."},{"time":750000,"text":"And it's kind of my favorite thing in the world."},{"time":753000,"text":"And it just began like in the beginning of February. So who knows?"},{"time":755000,"text":"And again, I don't say it's good, I just think it's not boring, right?"},{"time":759000,"text":"And here is the last bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":764000,"text":"(Video) IM: I have to tell you, I make buttermilk pancakes or buttermilk waffles all the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":768000,"text":"Chef: Do you?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":769000,"text":"IM: Yeah, but I can never find buttermilk, ever."}]},{"cues":[{"time":771000,"text":"Chef: Oh."}]},{"cues":[{"time":772000,"text":"IM: You can't find buttermilk at Citarella; you can't find buttermilk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":774000,"text":"Chef: You can't?"},{"time":775000,"text":"IM: It's always low-fat buttermilk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776000,"text":"Chef: No, but that's all it is."},{"time":777000,"text":"IM: Is that all it is?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":778000,"text":"Chef: Oh, you don't know? Let me tell you something."},{"time":780000,"text":"Let me tell you something interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":781000,"text":"IM: You know what? Stop laughing. It's not funny."},{"time":782000,"text":"Just because I don't know that whole -- that there's no such thing as whole buttermilk."},{"time":787000,"text":"Sorry, what?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":788000,"text":"Chef: Well, here's the deal. Let me tell you the deal."},{"time":789000,"text":"In the old days when they used to make butter,"},{"time":791000,"text":"you know how you make butter?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":792000,"text":"IM: Churns?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":793000,"text":"Chef: For cream?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"IM: Yeah, exactly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":795000,"text":"Chef: So you take heavy, high-fat milk, which is cream,"},{"time":798000,"text":"and you churn it until it separates into these curds and water."},{"time":803000,"text":"The liquid is actually that clear liquid."},{"time":805000,"text":"If you've ever overbeaten your whipped cream,"},{"time":806000,"text":"it's actually buttermilk."},{"time":809000,"text":"And that's what it was in the early days."},{"time":810000,"text":"And that's what people used for baking and all sorts of things."},{"time":813000,"text":"Now, the buttermilk that you get is actually low-fat or skim milk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":816000,"text":"IM: Excuse me, I didn't know. All right?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":818000,"text":"Chef: The reason he thought that is because buttermilk is so wonderfully thick and delicious."}]},{"cues":[{"time":823000,"text":"IM: Yeah, it is, exactly."},{"time":824000,"text":"So who would think that it was low-fat?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":826000,"text":"Well, that's it. Thank you very much."},{"time":829000,"text":"Happy TED. It's so wonderful here. I love it. I love it. I love it."},{"time":832000,"text":"Thanks. Bye."}]}]}